          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1612882758099-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Season the<strong> lean beef mixture</strong> with a generous grind of<strong> pepper</strong>, then transfer to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Top the beef mixture with the<strong> chips</strong></p><p>Tip: Try to put the crispiest chips at the bottom and balance the rest over the top so that they don’t sink!</p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 15-20 min or until the chips are crispy and cooked through – this is your <strong>chip-topped lean beef & thyme pie</strong></p>",
